{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853608521,"sessionID":"ses_286e0a496ffeAx3bF2slH4epid","part":{"id":"prt_d791f9df3001AcCWA5I9VYiiCy","messageID":"msg_d791f7bda001swX0MnXMBxE0nW","sessionID":"ses_286e0a496ffeAx3bF2slH4epid","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3f2faac042144504a4eec3cc618ded3b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Implement JWT authentication and signing capabilities for the AgentCube Router module. This provides secure service-to-service communication and identity verification between Router and sandbox pods. The JWT component:\n6: \n7: 1. **Token Generation**: Creates signed JWT tokens with RS256 algorithm containing session/sandbox identity claims\n8: 2. **Key Management**: Generates RSA key pairs (2048-bit) for signing and verification\n9: 3. **Token Claims**: Embeds session_id, sandbox_id, namespace, name as standard claims with 5-minute expiration\n10: 4. **Issuer Identity**: Sets `agentcube-router` as standard issuer for service identification\n11: 5. **Key Persistence**: Supports PEM encoding/decoding for Kubernetes Secret storage\n12: 6. **Public Key Distribution**: Provides GetPublicKey for downstream verification\n13: \n14: ## Scope\n15: \n16: ### In Scope\n17: \n18: | Deliverable | Description |\n19: |-------------|-------------|\n20: | `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWTManager implementation with GenerateToken, key management, PEM encoding |\n21: | `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | Unit tests for token generation, parsing, expiration, key encoding |\n22: | `pkg/router/errors.go` | JWTSigningError type with APIStatus implementation |\n23: | `pkg/router/doc.go` | JWTManagerInterface definition |\n24: | RSA Key Generation | 2048-bit RSA keys for RS256 signing |\n25: | Token Expiration | 5-minute default expiration (jwtExpiration constant) |\n26: | PEM Encoding | encodePrivateKeyPEM, encodePublicKeyPEM, loadPrivateKeyPEM helpers |\n27: | Kubernetes Secret Support | IdentitySecretName, PrivateKeyDataKey, PublicKeyDataKey constants |\n28: \n29: ### Key Components\n30: \n31: ```\n32: pkg/router/\n33: ├── JWTManager (jwt.go)\n34: │   ├── privateKey: *rsa.PrivateKey (2048-bit)\n35: │   ├── publicKey: *rsa.PublicKey\n36: │   ├── GenerateToken(claims): RS256 signed JWT with exp, iat, iss + custom claims\n37: │   ├── GetPublicKey(): Returns public key for verification\n38: │   └── TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx): Placeholder for K8s Secret persistence\n39: │\n40: ├── Constants (jwt.go)\n41: │   ├── rsaKeySize = 2048\n42: │   ├── jwtExpiration = 5 * time.Minute\n43: │   ├── IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n44: │   ├── PrivateKeyDataKey = \"private.pem\"\n45: │   ├── PublicKeyDataKey = \"public.pem\"\n46: │   └── IdentityNamespace = \"default\" (or AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE env)\n47: │\n48: ├── PEM Helpers (jwt.go)\n49: │   ├── encodePrivateKeyPEM(key): PKCS1 PEM format\n50: │   ├── encodePublicKeyPEM(key): PKIX PEM format\n51: │   └── loadPrivateKeyPEM(data): Parse PKCS1 PEM to rsa.PrivateKey\n52: │\n53: └── JWTSigningError (errors.go)\n54: │   ├── Err: wrapped error\n55: │   ├── Status() = 500\n56: │   ├── Code() = \"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"\n57: │   └── Message() = \"jwt signing failed\"\n58: ```\n59: \n60: ### Out of Scope\n61: \n62: - Token validation middleware (not needed; Router only generates, sandboxes verify)\n63: - OAuth2/OIDC protocol implementation\n64: - Third-party identity provider integration\n65: - Refresh token mechanism\n66: - Token revocation/blacklist\n67: - Fine-grained RBAC permissions\n68: - HS256 symmetric signing (RS256 asymmetric is preferred for distributed verification)\n69: \n70: ## Impact Analysis\n71: \n72: ### Upstream Dependencies\n73: \n74: | Dependency | Impact |\n75: |------------|--------|\n76: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | Core JWT library for token creation and parsing |\n77: | `crypto/rand` | Secure random number generation for RSA keys |\n78: | `crypto/rsa` | RSA key generation and signing |\n79: | `crypto/x509`, `encoding/pem` | PEM encoding for key storage |\n80: | `k8s.io/klog/v2` | Logging for TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret warning |\n81: | `os.Getenv` | AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE for IdentityNamespace |\n82: \n83: ### Downstream Consumers\n84: \n85: | Consumer | Usage |\n86: |----------|-------|\n87: | `Server.handleInvoke` | Calls jwtManager.GenerateToken with session/sandbox claims for sandbox/claim kinds |\n88: | `reverse_proxy.go` | JWT token added to Authorization header when proxying to sandbox |\n89: | Sandbox pods | Verify JWT using Router's public key (distributed via K8s Secret) |\n90: | `Server` struct | Stores *JWTManager for token generation |\n91: \n92: ### Breaking Change Considerations\n93: \n94: - **JWT Claims Schema**: session_id, sandbox_id, namespace, name claims are consumed by sandboxes; changing requires sandbox update\n95: - **Issuer Name**: `agentcube-router` is expected by verification logic; changing breaks trust\n96: - **Expiration Duration**: 5-minute jwtExpiration affects sandbox verification window\n97: - **Key Size**: 2048-bit RSA is expected; smaller keys may be rejected by validators\n98: - **Secret Name**: `picod-router-identity` Secret must exist for public key distribution\n99: \n100: ## Alternatives Considered\n101: \n102: ### Alternative 1: HS256 Symmetric Signing\n103: \n104: **Approach**: Use HMAC-SHA256 with shared secret key instead of RSA.\n105: \n106: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n107: |--------|------------|\n108: | Pros | Faster signing/verification; simpler key management (single secret) |\n109: | Cons | Secret must be shared with all verifiers; key rotation requires all services to update; less secure distribution |\n110: \n111: **Decision**: Rejected. RS256 asymmetric signing allows Router to keep private key secret while distributing public key to sandboxes. Key rotation only affects Router, not all verifiers.\n112: \n113: ### Alternative 2: Longer Token Expiration\n114: \n115: **Approach**: Use 24-hour or longer token expiration to reduce token generation overhead.\n116: \n117: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n118: |--------|------------|\n119: | Pros | Fewer token generations; simpler session handling |\n120: | Cons | Stale tokens persist longer; sandbox may accept requests after session ended; security risk |\n121: \n122: **Decision**: Rejected. 5-minute expiration aligns with short-lived sandbox sessions. Tokens naturally expire before or around session timeout (30 minutes default), reducing stale token acceptance.\n123: \n124: ### Alternative 3: JWT in Query Parameter\n125: \n126: **Approach**: Pass JWT token via URL query parameter instead of Authorization header.\n127: \n128: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n129: |--------|------------|\n130: | Pros | Simpler for HTTP clients without header support |\n131: | Cons | Token visible in URLs; logged in proxy/server logs; URL-encoded tokens break caching |\n132: \n133: **Decision**: Rejected. Authorization header (`Authorization: Bearer <token>`) is OAuth2/Bearer standard, keeps token out of URLs and logs.\n134: \n135: ### Alternative 4: External JWT Service\n136: \n137: **Approach**: Delegate JWT generation to external identity service (e.g., Auth0, Keycloak).\n138: \n139: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n140: |--------|------------|\n141: | Pros | Centralized identity management; standard OAuth2/OIDC support |\n142: | Cons | External dependency; network latency for each token; cost; overkill for service-to-service auth |\n143: \n144: **Decision**: Rejected. Router-to-sandbox auth is simple service identity, not user auth. Self-contained JWT generation keeps architecture simple and avoids external dependencies.\n145: \n146: ### Alternative 5: No JWT (Direct Service Account Auth)\n147: \n148: **Approach**: Use Kubernetes service account token for all authentication.\n149: \n150: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n151: |--------|------------|\n152: | Pros | K8s-native; no custom JWT code; automatic token rotation |\n153: | Cons | Service account tokens are long-lived (1 hour+); no sandbox-specific claims; shared across all pods with same SA |\n154: \n155: **Decision**: Rejected. Router JWT provides per-session claims (session_id, sandbox_id) for fine-grained sandbox identification. Service account tokens lack this granularity.\n156: \n157: ## Risks\n158: \n159: | Risk | Mitigation |\n160: |------|------------|\n161: | Private key leakage | Keep private key in Router memory; never log; use K8s Secret for persistence (read-only for sandboxes) |\n162: | Token replay attacks | Short 5-minute expiration; tokens tied to specific session/sandbox |\n163: | Clock drift causes validation failure | JWT library handles reasonable clock skew; sandboxes use jwt.WithLeeway() |\n164: | Key rotation disruption | TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret supports loading existing keys; generate new only on startup |\n165: | Public key unavailable to sandbox | Distribute via K8s Secret `picod-router-identity`; sandboxes mount as volume |\n166: | RSA key generation slow | Generate once at Router startup; reuse for all tokens |\n167: | Missing JWT claims | GenerateToken requires claims map; validation in sandbox verifies required fields |\n168: \n169: ## Implementation Notes\n170: \n171: 1. **Library**: `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` (latest stable)\n172: 2. **Algorithm**: RS256 (RSA Signature with SHA-256)\n173: 3. **Key Size**: 2048-bit RSA (balance of security and performance)\n174: 4. **Expiration**: 5 minutes (`jwtExpiration = 5 * time.Minute`)\n175: 5. **Issuer**: `agentcube-router` (standard `iss` claim)\n176: 6. **Claims**: Standard (exp, iat, iss) + Custom (session_id, sandbox_id, namespace, name)\n177: 7. **Namespace**: `IdentityNamespace = \"default\"` or from `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` env\n178: 8. **Secret Name**: `picod-router-identity` for K8s Secret containing PEM-encoded keys\n179: 9. **PEM Format**: Private key PKCS1, Public key PKIX (standard formats)\n180: 10. **Error Handling**: JWTSigningError wraps underlying error, returns 500 status\n181: \n182: ## References\n183: \n184: - [golang-jwt/jwt v5](https://github.com/golang-jwt/jwt)\n185: - [RFC 7519 - JSON Web Token](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)\n186: - [RFC 7518 - JSON Web Algorithms](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7518) (RS256)\n187: - `pkg/router/jwt.go` - Implementation\n188: - `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` - Test coverage\n189: - `pkg/router/doc.go` - JWTManagerInterface definition\n190: - `pkg/router/errors.go` - JWTSigningError type\n191: - `pkg/router/server.go:154-171` - JWT usage in handleInvoke\n192: - `deployment/client-go.md` - Kubernetes client reference (for Secret management)\n193: - `changes/AR-010/proposal.md` - Related Session Manager proposal\n\n(End of file - total 193 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\nImplement JWT authentication and signing capabilities for the AgentCube Router module. This provides secure service-to-service communication and identity verification between Router and sandbox pods. The JWT component:\n\n1. **Token Generation**: Creates signed JWT tokens with RS256 algorithm containing session/sandbox identity claims\n2. **Key Management**: Generates RSA key pairs (2048-bit) for signing and verification\n3. **Token Claims**: Embeds session_id, sandbox_id, namespace, name as standard claims with 5-minute expiration\n4. **Issuer Identity**: Sets `agentcube-router` as standard issuer for service identification\n5. **Key Persistence**: Supports PEM encoding/decoding for Kubernetes Secret storage\n6. **Public Key Distribution**: Provides GetPublicKey for downstream verification\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWTManager implementation with GenerateToken, key management, PEM encoding |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775853608470,"end":1775853608519}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853608524,"sessionID":"ses_286e0a496ffeAx3bF2slH4epid","part":{"id":"prt_d791f9a75001Sp6mKwlXqYiOZk","messageID":"msg_d791f7bda001swX0MnXMBxE0nW","sessionID":"ses_286e0a496ffeAx3bF2slH4epid","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-85c51027211b4748914dec6d00dfe704","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/router`\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Overview\n10: \n11: 为 Router 模块添加 JWT 认证与签发能力，包括 RSA 密钥生成、Token 签发、PEM 编解码、Kubernetes Secret 持久化等功能。JWT 用于在反向代理请求中注入认证信息，供下游 Sandbox Pod 验证请求来源。\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n16: \n17: ### Requirement: JWTManager 类型定义\n18: \n19: 系统 SHALL 定义 `JWTManager` 结构体用于 JWT Token 签发与密钥管理。\n20: \n21: #### Scenario: JWTManager struct 定义\n22: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n23: - **WHEN** 读取 `JWTManager` 结构体\n24: - **THEN** 结构体 SHALL 包含字段:\n25:   - `privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey` 用于 RSA 签名\n26:   - `publicKey *rsa.PublicKey` 用于签名验证\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: RSA 密钥大小常量\n29: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n30: - **WHEN** 读取常量定义\n31: - **THEN** `rsaKeySize` SHALL 为 `2048` bits\n32: \n33: #### Scenario: JWT 过期时间常量\n34: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n35: - **WHEN** 读取常量定义\n36: - **THEN** `jwtExpiration` SHALL 为 `5 * time.Minute`\n37: \n38: #### Scenario: Secret 名称常量\n39: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n40: - **WHEN** 读取常量定义\n41: - **THEN** `IdentitySecretName` SHALL 为 `\"picod-router-identity\"`\n42: - AND `PrivateKeyDataKey` SHALL 为 `\"private.pem\"`\n43: - AND `PublicKeyDataKey` SHALL 为 `\"public.pem\"`\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ### Requirement: JWTManager 构造函数\n48: \n49: 系统 SHALL 提供 `NewJWTManager` 构造函数生成 RSA 密钥对。\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: NewJWTManager 生成密钥对\n52: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n53: - **WHEN** 调用 `NewJWTManager()`\n54: - **THEN** RSA 密钥对 SHALL 通过 `rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, rsaKeySize)` 生成\n55: - AND 密钥大小 SHALL 为 `2048` bits\n56: - AND 返回 `*JWTManager` 包含 `privateKey` 和 `publicKey`\n57: - AND `publicKey` SHALL 为 `&privateKey.PublicKey`\n58: \n59: #### Scenario: NewJWTManager 密钥生成失败\n60: - **GIVEN** 系统熵不足或其他异常\n61: - **WHEN** `rsa.GenerateKey` 返回错误\n62: - **THEN** 构造函数 SHALL 返回 `nil` 和 `error`\n63: - AND 错误信息 SHALL 包含 `\"failed to generate RSA key\"`\n64: \n65: ---\n66: \n67: ### Requirement: Token 签发功能\n68: \n69: 系统 SHALL 提供 `GenerateToken` 方法生成 RS256 签名的 JWT Token。\n70: \n71: #### Scenario: GenerateToken 基本签发\n72: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go` 中的 `JWTManager`\n73: - **WHEN** 调用 `GenerateToken(claims map[string]interface{})`\n74: - **THEN** JWT Token SHALL 使用 `jwt.SigningMethodRS256` 算法\n75: - AND Token SHALL 包含标准 Claims:\n76:   - `exp` = `now + jwtExpiration` (5分钟过期)\n77:   - `iat` = `now` (签发时间)\n78:   - `iss` = `\"agentcube-router\"` (签发者)\n79: - AND 用户提供的 claims SHALL 合并到 Token Claims 中\n80: - AND Token SHALL 使用 `privateKey` 签名\n81: - AND 返回签名的 Token 字符串\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: GenerateToken 包含自定义 Claims\n84: - **GIVEN** 用户提供 claims `{\"session_id\": \"abc\", \"sandbox_id\": \"xyz\"}`\n85: - **WHEN** 调用 `GenerateToken(claims)`\n86: - **THEN** 生成的 Token SHALL 包含:\n87:   - `session_id` = `\"abc\"`\n88:   - `sandbox_id` = `\"xyz\"`\n89:   - 以及标准 Claims (`exp`, `iat`, `iss`)\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: GenerateToken 签名失败\n92: - **GIVEN** `jwt.SignedString` 返回错误\n93: - **WHEN** Token 签名过程失败\n94: - **THEN** SHALL 返回 `\"\"` 和 `JWTSigningError`\n95: - AND 错误 SHALL 包装底层错误\n96: \n97: #### Scenario: GenerateToken 过期时间计算\n98: - **GIVEN** 当前时间 `now`\n99: - **WHEN** 生成 Token\n100: - **THEN** `exp` Claim SHALL 为 `now.Unix() + int64(jwtExpiration.Seconds())`\n101: - AND 容差 SHALL 为 ±5秒\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: ### Requirement: PEM 编解码功能\n106: \n107: 系统 SHALL 提供 PEM 格式的 RSA 密钥编解码函数。\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: encodePrivateKeyPEM 编码私钥\n110: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n111: - **WHEN** 调用 `encodePrivateKeyPEM(key *rsa.PrivateKey)`\n112: - **THEN** 返回 PEM 格式字节\n113: - AND PEM Block Type SHALL 为 `\"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"`\n114: - AND 私钥 SHALL 使用 PKCS1 格式 (`x509.MarshalPKCS1PrivateKey`)\n115: - AND PEM 格式 SHALL 包含 `-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----`\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: encodePublicKeyPEM 编码公钥\n118: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n119: - **WHEN** 调用 `encodePublicKeyPEM(key *rsa.PublicKey)`\n120: - **THEN** 返回 PEM 格式字节\n121: - AND PEM Block Type SHALL 为 `\"PUBLIC KEY\"`\n122: - AND 公钥 SHALL 使用 PKIX 格式 (`x509.MarshalPKIXPublicKey`)\n123: - AND PEM 格式 SHALL 包含 `-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----`\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: encodePublicKeyPEM 编码失败\n126: - **GIVEN** `x509.MarshalPKIXPublicKey` 返回错误\n127: - **WHEN** 编码公钥失败\n128: - **THEN** 函数 SHALL 返回 `nil`\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: loadPrivateKeyPEM 解码私钥\n131: - **GIVEN** PEM 格式的私钥字节\n132: - **WHEN** 调用 `loadPrivateKeyPEM(data []byte)`\n133: - **THEN** SHALL 使用 `pem.Decode` 解析 PEM Block\n134: - AND SHALL 使用 `x509.ParsePKCS1PrivateKey` 解析私钥\n135: - AND 返回 `*rsa.PrivateKey` 和 `nil` error\n136: \n137: #### Scenario: loadPrivateKeyPEM PEM 解析失败\n138: - **GIVEN** 无效 PEM 数据\n139: - **WHEN** `pem.Decode` 返回 `nil` Block\n140: - **THEN** SHALL 返回 `nil` 和 error\n141: - AND 错误信息 SHALL 为 `\"failed to decode PEM block\"`\n142: \n143: #### Scenario: loadPrivateKeyPEM 私钥解析失败\n144: - **GIVEN** 有效 PEM Block 但无效私钥数据\n145: - **WHEN** `x509.ParsePKCS1PrivateKey` 失败\n146: - **THEN** SHALL 返回 `nil` 和 error\n147: - AND 错误信息 SHALL 包含 `\"failed to parse private key\"`\n148: \n149: ---\n150: \n151: ### Requirement: 公钥获取功能\n152: \n153: 系统 SHALL 提供 `GetPublicKey` 方法获取 RSA 公钥。\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: GetPublicKey 返回公钥\n156: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go` 中的 `JWTManager`\n157: - **WHEN** 调用 `GetPublicKey()`\n158: - **THEN** SHALL 返回 `*rsa.PublicKey`\n159: - AND 公钥大小 SHALL 为 `2048/8 = 256` bytes\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: GetPublicKey 用于验证\n162: - **GIVEN** Token 使用 RS256 签名\n163: - **WHEN** 使用 `jwt.Parse` 验证 Token\n164: - **THEN** `GetPublicKey()` 返回的公钥 SHALL 用于签名验证\n165: \n166: ---\n167: \n168: ### Requirement: Secret 持久化功能\n169: \n170: 系统 SHALL 提供 `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret` 方法在 Kubernetes 中持久化密钥。\n171: \n172: #### Scenario: TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret 基本行为\n173: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n174: - **WHEN** 调用 `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx context.Context)`\n175: - **THEN** SHALL 尝试在 Kubernetes 中存储/加载密钥 Secret\n176: - AND Secret 名称 SHALL 为 `IdentitySecretName` (`\"picod-router-identity\"`)\n177: - AND Secret Namespace SHALL 为 `IdentityNamespace`\n178: \n179: #### Scenario: TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret 非集群环境\n180: - **GIVEN** 非 Kubernetes 集群环境运行\n181: - **WHEN** 调用 `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret`\n182: - **THEN** SHALL 使用 `klog.Warningf` 记录 `\"not in cluster, skipping secret persistence\"`\n183: - AND 返回 `nil` error\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: IdentityNamespace 环境变量\n186: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt.go` init 函数\n187: - **WHEN** 系统启动\n188: - **THEN** SHALL 读取 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` 环境变量\n189: - AND 默认 `IdentityNamespace` SHALL 为 `\"default\"`\n190: - AND 若环境变量设置，`IdentityNamespace` SHALL 使用该值\n191: \n192: ---\n193: \n194: ### Requirement: JWTSigningError 错误类型\n195: \n196: 系统 SHALL 定义 `JWTSigningError` 错误类型用于 JWT 签名失败。\n197: \n198: #### Scenario: JWTSigningError struct 定义\n199: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/errors.go`\n200: - **WHEN** 读取 `JWTSigningError` 结构体\n201: - **THEN** 结构体 SHALL 包含字段:\n202:   - `Err error` 用于包装底层错误\n203: \n204: #### Scenario: JWTSigningError Error 方法\n205: - **GIVEN** `JWTSigningError` 实例\n206: - **WHEN** 调用 `Error()` 方法\n207: - **THEN** 返回字符串 SHALL 为 `\"jwt signing failed: \" + e.Err.Error()`\n208: \n209: #### Scenario: JWTSigningError Status 方法\n210: - **GIVEN** `JWTSigningError` 实例\n211: - **WHEN** 调用 `Status()` 方法\n212: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP Status SHALL 为 `500`\n213: \n214: #### Scenario: JWTSigningError Code 方法\n215: - **GIVEN** `JWTSigningError` 实例\n216: - **WHEN** 调用 `Code()` 方法\n217: - **THEN** 返回错误码 SHALL 为 `\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"`\n218: \n219: #### Scenario: JWTSigningError Message 方法\n220: - **GIVEN** `JWTSigningError` 实例\n221: - **WHEN** 调用 `Message()` 方法\n222: - **THEN** 返回消息 SHALL 为 `\"jwt signing failed\"`\n223: \n224: ---\n225: \n226: ### Requirement: JWT Token 验证场景\n227: \n228: 系统 SHALL 支持 JWT Token 的外部验证。\n229: \n230: #### Scenario: 使用公钥验证 Token\n231: - **GIVEN** 通过 `GenerateToken` 生成的 Token\n232: - **WHEN** 使用 `jwt.Parse` 和 `GetPublicKey()` 验证\n233: - **THEN** Token SHALL 被成功解析\n234: - AND `token.Valid` SHALL 为 `true`\n235: - AND Claims SHALL 包含所有自定义字段\n236: \n237: #### Scenario: 拒绝无效签名 Token\n238: - **GIVEN** 使用错误私钥签名的 Token\n239: - **WHEN** 使用正确公钥验证\n240: - **THEN** SHALL 返回 `jwt.ErrSignatureInvalid` 错误\n241: \n242: #### Scenario: 拒绝过期 Token\n243: - **GIVEN** 已超过 `jwtExpiration` (5分钟) 的 Token\n244: - **WHEN** 验证 Token\n245: - **THEN** SHALL 返回过期错误\n246: \n247: #### Scenario: 签名方法验证\n248: - **GIVEN** Token 使用非 RSA 签名方法\n249: - **WHEN** 解析 Token\n250: - **THEN** SHALL 返回 `jwt.ErrSignatureInvalid` 错误\n251: \n252: ---\n253: \n254: ### Requirement: JWT 在反向代理中的使用\n255: \n256: 系统 SHALL 在反向代理请求中注入 JWT Token。\n257: \n258: #### Scenario: handleInvoke JWT 生成\n259: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/server.go` 的 `handleInvoke` 方法\n260: - **WHEN** 处理 Sandbox/Claim 类请求\n261: - **THEN** `jwtManager.GenerateToken` SHALL 被调用\n262: - AND Claims SHALL 包含:\n263:   - `session_id` = `sandbox.SessionID`\n264:   - `sandbox_id` = `sandbox.SandboxID`\n265:   - `namespace` = `sandbox.SandboxNamespace`\n266:   - `name` = `sandbox.SandboxName`\n267: \n268: #### Scenario: handleInvoke JWT 注入 Header\n269: - **GIVEN** 生成的 JWT Token\n270: - **WHEN** 反向代理转发请求\n271: - **THEN** `Authorization: Bearer <jwt>` Header SHALL 被添加\n272: \n273: #### Scenario: handleInvoke JWT 签名失败\n274: - **GIVEN** `GenerateToken` 返回错误\n275: - **WHEN** JWT 签名失败\n276: - **THEN** HTTP `500` SHALL 被返回\n277: - AND 响应 SHALL 包含 `{\"error\": \"jwt signing failed\", \"code\": \"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"}`\n278: \n279: ---\n280: \n281: ### Requirement: 单元测试覆盖\n282: \n283: 系统 SHALL 有全面的 JWT 功能单元测试。\n284: \n285: #### Scenario: TestNewJWTManager 测试\n286: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n287: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n288: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n289:   - `JWTManager` 构造成功\n290:   - `privateKey` 非 nil\n291:   - `publicKey` 非 nil\n292: \n293: #### Scenario: TestJWTManagerGenerateToken 测试\n294: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n295: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n296: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n297:   - Token 生成成功\n298:   - Token 可被正确解析验证\n299:   - Token 包含正确的自定义 Claims\n300:   - Token 签发者 `iss` = `\"agentcube-router\"`\n301: \n302: #### Scenario: TestJWTManagerTokenExpiration 测试\n303: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n304: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n305: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n306:   - Token 过期时间正确设置\n307:   - `exp` Claim 约为 `now + 5m`\n308:   - Token 未过期\n309: \n310: #### Scenario: TestJWTManagerGetPublicKey 测试\n311: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n312: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n313: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n314:   - `GetPublicKey` 返回非 nil\n315:   - 公钥大小为 `2048/8 = 256` bytes\n316: \n317: #### Scenario: TestEncodePrivateKeyPEM 测试\n318: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n319: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n320: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n321:   - PEM 编码返回非 nil\n322:   - PEM 数据包含 `\"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"`\n323: \n324: #### Scenario: TestEncodePublicKeyPEM 测试\n325: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n326: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n327: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n328:   - PEM 编码返回非 nil\n329:   - PEM 数据包含 `\"PUBLIC KEY\"`\n330: \n331: #### Scenario: TestLoadPrivateKeyPEM 测试\n332: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n333: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n334: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n335:   - PEM 解码成功\n336:   - 加载的私钥与原始私钥匹配 (`N.Cmp` = 0)\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: TestLoadPrivateKeyPEMInvalid 测试\n339: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n340: - **WHEN** 使用无效 PEM 数据运行测试\n341: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证返回错误\n342: \n343: #### Scenario: TestJWTSigningError 测试\n344: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/errors_test.go`\n345: - **WHEN** 运行测试\n346: - **THEN** 测试 SHALL 验证:\n347:   - `Error()` 方法返回正确字符串\n348:   - `Code()` 返回 `\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"`\n349:   - `Message()` 返回 `\"jwt signing failed\"`\n350:   - `Status()` 返回 `500`\n351: \n352: ---\n353: \n354: ### Requirement: 文件结构\n355: \n356: 系统 SHALL 正确组织 JWT 相关文件。\n357: \n358: #### Scenario: jwt.go 位置\n359: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/`\n360: - **WHEN** 列出文件\n361: - **THEN** `jwt.go` SHALL 存在，包含 JWTManager 实现\n362: \n363: #### Scenario: jwt_test.go 位置\n364: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/`\n365: - **WHEN** 列出文件\n366: - **THEN** `jwt_test.go` SHALL 存在，包含单元测试\n367: \n368: #### Scenario: errors.go JWTSigningError\n369: - **GIVEN** `pkg/router/errors.go`\n370: - **WHEN** 读取文件\n371: - **THEN** `JWTSigningError` SHALL 定义\n372: \n373: ---\n374: \n375: ## Implementation Files\n376: \n377: | File | Purpose |\n378: |------|---------|\n379: | `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWTManager 结构体、GenerateToken、PEM 编解码、Secret 持久化 |\n380: | `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | JWT 功能单元测试 |\n381: | `pkg/router/errors.go` | JWTSigningError 错误类型定义 |\n382: | `pkg/router/errors_test.go` | 错误类型单元测试 |\n383: | `pkg/router/server.go` | handleInvoke 中 JWT 生成与注入 |\n384: | `pkg/router/reverse_proxy.go` | Director 中 JWT Header 设置 |\n385: \n386: ---\n387: \n388: ## Dependencies\n389: \n390: | Package | Purpose |\n391: |---------|---------|\n392: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | JWT 标准 Claims 和 RS256 签名 |\n393: | `crypto/rsa` | RSA 密钥生成和签名 |\n394: | `crypto/rand` | 安全随机数生成器 |\n395: | `crypto/x509` | PKCS1/PKIX 密钥编解码 |\n396: | `encoding/pem` | PEM 格式编解码 |\n397: | `k8s.io/klog/v2` | 结构化日志 |\n398: | `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes` | Kubernetes Secret 操作 |\n399: | `net/http` | HTTP 客户端和反向代理 |\n400: \n401: ---\n402: \n403: ## JWT Claims 结构\n404: \n405: | Claim | 类型 | 来源 | 描述 |\n406: |-------|------|------|------|\n407: | `exp` | int64 | 自动生成 | 过期时间 (now + 5m) |\n408: | `iat` | int64 | 自动生成 | 签发时间 (now) |\n409: | `iss` | string | 固定值 | 签发者 `\"agentcube-router\"` |\n410: | `session_id` | string | 用户传入 | Session ID |\n411: | `sandbox_id` | string | 用户传入 | Sandbox ID |\n412: | `namespace` | string | 用户传入 | Sandbox Namespace |\n413: | `name` | string | 用户传入 | Sandbox Name |\n414: \n415: ---\n416: \n417: ## Constants\n418: \n419: | 常量 | 值 | 用途 |\n420: |------|-----|------|\n421: | `rsaKeySize` | `2048` | RSA 密钥大小 (bits) |\n422: | `jwtExpiration` | `5 * time.Minute` | Token 有效期 |\n423: | `IdentitySecretName` | `\"picod-router-identity\"` | Kubernetes Secret 名称 |\n424: | `PrivateKeyDataKey` | `\"private.pem\"` | Secret 中私钥数据键 |\n425: | `PublicKeyDataKey` | `\"public.pem\"` | Secret 中公钥数据键 |\n426: | `IdentityNamespace` | `\"default\"` (可配置) | Secret Namespace |\n427: \n428: ---\n429: \n430: ## Environment Variables\n431: \n432: | 变量 | 必需 | 默认值 | 用途 |\n433: |------|------|--------|------|\n434: | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | No | `\"default\"` | JWT Secret 存储的 Namespace |\n435: \n436: ---\n437: \n438: ## Request Flow with JWT\n439: \n440: ```\n441: handleInvoke (server.go)\n442: │\n443: ├── 获取 SandboxInfo\n444: │\n445: ├── JWT Generation (if kind == Sandbox/Claim)\n446: │   │\n447: │   ├── jwtManager.GenerateToken(claims)\n448: │   │   ├── 创建 MapClaims\n449: │   │   │   ├── exp = now + 5m\n450: │   │   │   ├── iat = now\n451: │   │   │   ├── iss = \"agentcube-router\"\n452: │   │   │   ├── session_id, sandbox_id, namespace, name\n453: │   │   │\n454: │   │   ├── jwt.NewWithClaims(SigningMethodRS256)\n455: │   │   ├── token.SignedString(privateKey)\n456: │   │   │\n457: │   │   └── Return JWT string\n458: │   │\n459: │   └── Error: JWTSigningError\n460: │       ├── Status: 500\n461: │       ├── Code: \"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"\n462: │       └── Message: \"jwt signing failed\"\n463: │\n464: ├── ReverseProxy.ServeHTTP\n465: │   │\n466: │   ├── Director (reverse_proxy.go)\n467: │   │   ├── req.Header.Set(\"Authorization\", \"Bearer \"+jwt)\n468: │   │   └── Forward to sandbox pod\n469: │   │\n470: │   └── Sandbox Pod validates JWT\n471: │       ├── Parse with publicKey\n472: │       ├── Verify RS256 signature\n473: │       ├── Check exp claim\n474: │       └── Extract session/sandbox info\n475: │\n476: └── Response\n477: ```\n478: \n479: ---\n480: \n481: ## Validation Checklist\n482: \n483: - [ ] JWTManager 结构体定义包含 privateKey 和 publicKey\n484: - [ ] rsaKeySize 常量为 2048\n485: - [ ] jwtExpiration 常量为 5 分钟\n486: - [ ] IdentitySecretName 常量为 \"picod-router-identity\"\n487: - [ ] NewJWTManager 生成有效 RSA 密钥对\n488: - [ ] GenerateToken 使用 RS256 算法\n489: - [ ] GenerateToken 包含 exp, iat, iss Claims\n490: - [ ] GenerateToken 合并用户 Claims\n491: - [ ] GenerateToken 失败返回 JWTSigningError\n492: - [ ] encodePrivateKeyPEM 使用 PKCS1 格式\n493: - [ ] encodePublicKeyPEM 使用 PKIX 格式\n494: - [ ] loadPrivateKeyPEM 解析 PKCS1 私钥\n495: - [ ] loadPrivateKeyPEM 处理无效数据错误\n496: - [ ] GetPublicKey 返回 RSA 公钥\n497: - [ ] TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret 在非集群环境跳过\n498: - [ ] IdentityNamespace 从 AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 读取\n499: - [ ] JWTSigningError 实现 APIStatus 接口\n500: - [ ] JWTSigningError.Error 返回正确格式\n501: - [ ] JWTSigningError.Status 返回 500\n502: - [ ] JWTSigningError.Code 返回 \"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"\n503: - [ ] handleInvoke 为 Sandbox/Claim 生成 JWT\n504: - [ ] JWT 注入 Authorization Header\n505: - [ ] JWT 签名失败返回 500 响应\n506: - [ ] 单元测试覆盖所有 JWT 功能\n507: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n508: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n509: - [ ] 测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n\n(End of file - total 509 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n**Module:** `pkg/router`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** M\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\n为 Router 模块添加 JWT 认证与签发能力，包括 RSA 密钥生成、Token 签发、PEM 编解码、Kubernetes Secret 持久化等功能。JWT 用于在反向代理请求中注入认证信息，供下游 Sandbox Pod 验证请求来源。\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: JWTManager 类型定义\n\n系统 SHALL 定义 `JWTManager` 结构体用于 JWT Token 签发与密钥管理。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775853608467,"end":1775853608522}}}}
