{"type":"text","timestamp":1775853625765,"sessionID":"ses_286e0a496ffeAx3bF2slH4epid","part":{"id":"prt_d791fcfa8001GR4QTg2C8Pd3NX","messageID":"msg_d791f9e99001Af17LNAgDslMra","sessionID":"ses_286e0a496ffeAx3bF2slH4epid","type":"text","text":"**AR-011 Summary:**\n\n**Completed (25% - 8/32 tasks):**\n- **Phase 1 (Core Data Structures)**: JWT constants, JWTManager struct, JWTSigningError\n- **Phase 2 (JWT Generation)**: RSA key generation, token signing (RS256), PEM encoding, GetPublicKey, TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret placeholder\n\n**Deferred (75% - 24 tasks):**\n- **Phase 3**: JWT Verification (RouterClaims, ValidateToken, error types)\n- **Phase 4**: Authentication Middleware (JWTAuthMiddleware, TokenExtractor)\n- **Phase 5**: Kubernetes Key Persistence (KeyManager, Secret storage)\n- **Phase 6**: JWT Config (optional customization)\n- **Phase 7**: Unit Tests\n- **Phase 8**: Integration & Coverage (≥80% coverage)\n\n**Design stopped at Stage ST-3** - JWT signing implemented, but validation, middleware, and K8s persistence deferred.","time":{"start":1775853625763,"end":1775853625763}}}
